Package groupproject

Class ReservationManager

java.lang.Object
groupproject.ReservationManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
Indexable
public class ReservationManager extends Object implements Indexable
Implements methods to allow creation, search and deletion of reservations. Reads stored reservations from text file upon instantiation, writes to text file every time reservations are created or deleted.
Author:
Tan Yu Ling, Shenal Devinda
